---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Map interactive page elements with @refs

Usage: bl map [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --selector <selector>  Scope to elements within this CSS selector
  -v, --verbose              Enable debug logging
      --headless             Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json                 Output as JSON
  -h, --help                 Print help

Examples:
  bl map
  # Lists interactive elements with refs like @e1, @e2
  # Use refs with other commands: bl click @e1

  bl map --selector "nav"
  # Only map elements inside the <nav> element
